article_title: Photos: Health dangers don't worry e-cig users
article_text:
Health dangers don't worry e-cig users

E-cigarettes are increasingly popular in the Milwaukee area, where businesses are popping up with names like Planet of the Vapes and Vape Escape. However, in a series of interviews, none of the employees or customers expressed concerns about potential dangers from e-cigarettes, many of which contain the chemical diacetyl.
